    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver that's easy on the wallet? This vehicle is in fair condition and ready for many more miles! While it shows some honest signs of its journey so far, it remains a reliable and practical choice for anyone needing a solid set of wheels at a great price.",
